reviews.review_text:
Ah, the memories... Good to hear this again my friends,
Jack

Jack? Jack, that gave me about 500 cassettes, over time, over 20 years ago, and I haven't seen in over 15 years?  Jack, that gave me this very recording before I ever knew Lance?!  Ha!  I sure hope so..?  I've missed that guy, for sure...
